<P>AN ORATION, ON PARTY SPIRIT, PRONOUNCED BEFORE THE CONNECTICUT SOCIETY OF CINCINNATI, CONVENED AT HARTFORD, FOR THE CELEBRATION OF AMERICAN INDEPENDENCE, ON THE <HI>4</HI>th of JULY, <HI>1798.</HI></P>
<P>BY THOMAS DAY.</P>
<P>PRINTED AT LITCHFIELD BY T. COLLIER.</P>
