<P>At a Meeting of the Connecticut State Society of the Cincinnati, at Hartford, on the Fourth Day of July, 1798.</P>
<P><HI>VOTED,</HI> That the Secretary present the Thanks of this Society to <HI>Thomas Day,</HI> Esq. for the <HI>Oration</HI> spoken by him this Day, before the Society, and that he request a Copy of the same for Publication, at the Expence of the Society.</P>
